WEBVTT

00:00:27.768 --> 00:00:31.467
da je barem bilo misteriozno.

00:00:32.792 --> 00:00:35.973
Jasnoća ili misterioznost?

00:00:35.973 --> 00:00:40.199
Balansiram između ovih dviju krajnosti
na poslu grafičkog dizajnera,

00:00:40.199 --> 00:00:45.031
ali i u svakodnevnom životu Njujorčanina

00:00:45.031 --> 00:00:46.561
svaki dan.

00:00:46.561 --> 00:00:51.028
Fasciniraju me dva elementa.

00:00:51.028 --> 00:00:53.390
Evo primjer.

00:00:53.390 --> 00:00:57.170
Koliko vas zna što je ovo?

00:00:59.703 --> 00:01:04.727
Dobro. A sada?